@startuml JWT_Token_Flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam linetype ortho

title JWT Token Flow: Register/Login hingga Penggunaan

participant "Browser\nUser" as User
participant "Frontend\nVue.js" as Frontend
participant "axios\nHTTP Client" as Axios
participant "Backend\nExpress API" as Backend
participant "JWT Utils" as JWT
participant "MongoDB" as DB
participant "Browser\nLocalStorage" as Storage

== STEP 1: LOGIN/REGISTER ==

User -> Frontend: 1. Input email\n& password
User -> Frontend: 2. Click\n"Login" button
Frontend -> Axios: 3. POST /api/auth/login\n{email, password}
Axios -> Backend: 4. HTTP Request\nto backend

Backend -> DB: 5. Query: cari user\ndengan email ini
DB --> Backend: 6. Return user\ndokumen

Backend -> Backend: 7. Verify password\nbcryptjs.compare()
alt Password Valid
  Backend -> JWT: 8. Generate JWT\njwt.sign(\n{id: user._id},\nsecret,\n{expiresIn: "7d"}\n)
  JWT --> Backend: 9. Return token\n"eyJhbGci...xy"
else Password Invalid
  Backend --> Axios: ❌ Return 401\nUnauthorized
  Axios --> Frontend: Error message
end

Backend -> Backend: 10. Build response
Backend --> Axios: 11. Return 200 OK\n{\n  "token": "eyJ...",\n  "user": {...}\n}

== STEP 2: SAVE TOKEN ==

Axios --> Frontend: Response received
Frontend -> Frontend: 12. Extract token\nfrom response
Frontend -> Storage: 13. localStorage.setItem(\n"token",\nresponse.data.token\n)
Storage --> Frontend: ✅ Token saved!

Frontend -> Storage: 14. localStorage.setItem(\n"user",\nJSON.stringify(user)\n)

note right of Storage
  Browser LocalStorage sekarang berisi:
  ├─ "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..."
  └─ "user": "{\"id\":\"507f...\",\"name\":\"John...\"}"

  Token ini persistent meski tab ditutup!
end note

== STEP 3: USE TOKEN (Setiap API Request) ==

Frontend -> Frontend: 15. User navigate\nke /dashboard
Frontend -> Axios: 16. GET /api/vehicles\n(request baru)

note right of Axios
  Axios Interceptor:
  ├─ const token = localStorage.getItem("token")
  ├─ config.headers.Authorization = `Bearer ${token}`
  └─ Proceed dengan request
end note

Axios -> Axios: 17. Read token\nfrom localStorage
Axios -> Axios: 18. Add to header:\nAuthorization:\nBearer eyJhbGci...

Axios -> Backend: 19. HTTP Request\nwith Authorization\nheader

Backend -> Backend: 20. Extract token\nfrom Authorization\nheader

Backend -> JWT: 21. Verify JWT\njwt.verify(\ntoken,\nsecret\n)
alt Token Valid & Not Expired
  JWT --> Backend: 22. ✅ Valid!\nReturn decoded:\n{id: user_id, iat, exp}
  Backend -> Backend: 23. Set req.user\n= decoded payload
  Backend -> DB: 24. Query vehicles\nmilk user ini
  DB --> Backend: 25. Return vehicles
  Backend --> Axios: 26. Return 200\n+ vehicles data
else Token Invalid or Expired
  JWT --> Backend: ❌ Invalid or Expired!
  Backend --> Axios: ❌ Return 401\nUnauthorized
end

Axios --> Frontend: 27. Response received
Frontend -> Frontend: 28. Update UI\nwith data

== STEP 4: LOGOUT ==

User -> Frontend: 29. Click\n"Logout" button
Frontend -> Storage: 30. localStorage\n.removeItem("token")
Frontend -> Storage: 31. localStorage\n.removeItem("user")
Storage --> Frontend: ✅ Token deleted!

Frontend -> Frontend: 32. Redirect to\n/login page

note bottom of Storage
  Sekarang tidak ada token di browser,
  setiap request ke API akan return 401
  User harus login lagi untuk mendapat token baru
end note

@enduml
